Class SSCResources.Query

java.lang.Object
  ssc.SSCResources.Query
Enclosing class:
SSCResources
public static final class SSCResources.Query
extends java.lang.Object

This is the keys for the query string following the url. Which key(s) is relevant and allowed depend on the type of request.

public static final java.lang.String RESPONSE
